title: can't view my profile
body: when I log in and play game or start a game and then when I click on my summoner profile its not showing up and if that works I can't see my match history any fix for this I look at riot support centar but nothing came up are there any fix for this does this happen to some 1 else?

replies.body: Are you able to load up anything else on the client like hextech or another player's profile?  What happens if you try relogging?  Also curious to know if you are on the updated or legacy client.  Let me know!

1st I tryd to see ather player profile it didn't work and hextech its fine its just profile and then I try to relogging and its fine the 1st time then when I start for queue it doesn't work and I am not on the client
